Interface QueryMapper<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of class being mapped
    All Superinterfaces:
    PlotStrategy
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    LabelledQueryMapper<F>

    public interface QueryMapper<T>
extends PlotStrategy
    Formatting object that gather the data for an arbitrary date range from a target object. Where RangeMapper is applied to individual data items QueryMapper is applied to factory classes that can perform more high level queries.
